        <Parent_String>printing-out paper [300127375], photographic paper [300014190], paper by function [300014146], paper (fiber product) [300014109], fiber by product [300014062], fiber and fiber by product [300014023], materials by physical form [300247256], materials by form [300014611], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
